search: 
sense XXX marker 3 else walk
move else search
pickup else search
goto home1
walk:
flip 3 else searchright
turn left
goto search
searchright:
flip 2 else searchstraight
turn right
goto search
searchstraight:
move else walk
goto search
home1:
sense ahead home else walkhome
move else home1
drop
goto search
walkhome:
flip 3 else walkhomeright
turn left
goto home1
walkhomeright:
flip 2 else walkhomestraight
turn right
goto home1
walkhomestraight:
move else walkhome
goto home1
